Sasquatch Cc Sasquatch is now saved out into O erms intra financialsdb Please save it onto your c drive before using it I made one quick adjustment There is no need to put in your cpr dollars and volumes to get your wacog The program will calculate your UA daybyday and the Pls calculate the values You still need to put in your wacogs in the Pls Again please send me all wishes about the program and I will try to accomodate all requests I would like to roll the final product out to everyone in two weeks and plan to have a brown bag on it at that time In the meantime please feel free to ask me any questions about the program Thanks again for your attention Pat

FW KStarr Swiss Re Rebooking UpdatePST Original Message From Palmer B Scott Sent Monday August PM To Ryder Patrick Subject FW KStarr Swiss Re Rebooking Update Original Message From Boyt Eric Sent Monday August AM To Keiser Kam Winfree ONeal D Mills Bruce Palmer B Scott Love Phillip M Cc Gossett Jeffrey C Diamond Russell Cook Mary Koehler Anne C Jones Doug Khan Rafi Wolfe Tony Subject RE KStarr Swiss Re Rebooking Update To all I got clearance from the lawyers that the KCSSwiss Re transaction did closed on Friday afternoon PLEASE ENDDATE THE EXISTING DEALS JULY AND UNTEMP THE NEW LEGS TODAY AUGUST th as discussed last week Attached is a spreadsheet Russell put together with the history of the TAGG s for your reference Call with any questions Eric x PS After you calc today I would appreciate a minibook with the new legs Thanks in advance for all your help Original Message From Boyt Eric Sent Thursday August PM To Keiser Kam Winfree ONeal D Mills Bruce Palmer B Scott Love Phillip M Cc Gossett Jeffrey C Diamond Russell Cook Mary Koehler Anne C Subject KStarr Swiss Re Rebooking Update Just to be clear Please DO NOT untemp the new legs to Swiss Re until you hear from Russell or myself Our lawyers are still negotiating the ISDA and will inform us as soon as it is signed We understand that if the documents are signed after pm today CST the deals will not be moved over until tomorrow However this does not appear to be an issue as nothing will be settling on the swaps until the end of September Please call with any questions Eric x
